data.description: Nestled on the outskirts of Longview you'll find this quaint and charming property sitting on 1.996 acres. This is a home that checks all of the boxes! The property not only sits on a hefty amount of acreage outside of Longview - it also boast a 2,900+ square foot home, refreshing pool and 2,000 square foot shop. All you need to do is move in! The well-designed floor plan seamlessly flows from the main living area to the separate formal dining and kitchen/breakfast nook. Primary bedroom is split on the first floor along with two guest bedrooms that have a shared bathroom. Venture upstairs, where you'll discover a bonus bedroom accompanied by a sizable living area, kitchenette and half bath - perfectly suited for a suite or office space. The interior leaves nothing to be desired, and the exterior is equally impressive, featuring expansive acreage, a pool, and a substantial shop. The 2,000 square foot workshop located at the rear of the property is fully insulated and comes equipped with plumbing and electric. This unique property is a rare gem waiting to be discovered in Longview!
